蝎子队推迟了鼓手 Mikkey Dee 因病康复而在拉斯维加斯举行的驻场演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/scorpions-postpone-las-vegas-residency-for-drummer-mikkey-dee-to-recover-from-illness-3830232?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=scorpions-推迟鼓手米基迪在拉斯维加斯居住以从疾病中恢复Surej SinghMon, 20 Jan 2025 03:17:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3830232 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Dee 曾经为 Motörhead 鼓手，今年早些时候透露，他最近因败血症住院，差点死于这种情况</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scorpions-postpone-las-vegas-residency-for-drummer-mikkey-dee-to-recover-from-illness-3830232">蝎子乐队推迟鼓手 Mikkey Dee 因病康复而推迟在拉斯维加斯驻场的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/scorpions-mikkey-dee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>蝎子乐队宣布推迟即将举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scorpions-announce-2025-las-vegas-residency-to-celebrate-60th-anniversary-buy-tickets-3797060">60 周年拉斯维加斯驻场</a>演出，以便让鼓手 Mikkey Dee 从病中康复。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/lemmy-biopic-motorhead-hawkwind-2690187"><b>“Lemmy”：Motörhead 传记片应包含的 7 个传奇故事</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>今年早些时候（1 月 2 日），鼓手 Mikkey Dee 曾为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motorhead">Motörhead</a>担任鼓手，直到 2015 年乐队在传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lemmy">Lemmy Kilmister</a>去世后解散。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/motorheads-mikkey-dee-almost-died-from-sepsis-and-was-nearly-playing-drums-with-lemmy-in-heaven-3825681">他透露，他最近因败血症（一种严重而危险的血液感染）住院治疗。</a> 。</p><p>他透露，他已经接受了各种手术，现已回家并正在康复中，但他曾一度濒临死亡。他在扭伤脚踝后发现了这种情况，并在去年 12 月表示：“立即进行了手术，这是三次手术中的第一个。他们把死去的、感染的和严重感染的东西都砍掉了。这对我来说并不是一次美好的旅程……有一天，我会在天堂里和莱米一起打鼓。我可以这么说。” </p><figure id="attachment_3825687" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825687" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825687" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing.jpg" alt="米基·迪伊 (Mikkey Dee) 在 Scorpion 的“摇滚信徒”巡演期间登台表演。 （丹尼尔·奈顿/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mikey-Dee-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825687" class="wp-caption-text">米基·迪伊 (Mikkey Dee) 在 Scorpion 的“摇滚信徒”巡演期间登台表演。 （丹尼尔·奈顿/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>上周末，Mikkey 自 2016 年以来一直为 Scorpions 打鼓的 Scorpions 在社交媒体上确认，他们将推迟在拉斯维加斯的驻场演出，以便 Dee 有更多时间康复。</p><p>该驻场计划最初宣布于二月进行，但现在将于八月开始。他们写道：“我们遗憾地通知您，由于 Mikkey Dee 最近的住院治疗仍在康复中，我们决定将拉斯维加斯驻地归来推迟到 2025 年 8 月。我们兄弟的健康和福祉非常重要。”最重要的是。我们祝愿 Mikkey 早日康复，并期待很快再次与大家一起摇滚！”</p><p>已购买的驻场门票将在新日期生效 - <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fscorpions-tickets%2Fartist%2F736062" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处获取门票</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE7y7WEB2di/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" strok