025/01/olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>已确认参加本月晚些时候在洛杉矶举行的 FireAid 慈善音乐会。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="840" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259"><b>洛杉矶音乐界告诉我们野火的“悲剧性”影响：“这种影响将持续多年”</b></a></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benefit-concert-for-victims-of-los-angeles-wildfires-announced-3828097">该活动于本月早些时候首次宣布，</a>旨在支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">洛杉矶毁灭性野火的受害者</a>，并将于 1 月 30 日在 Intuit Dome 和 KIA 论坛举行—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-lady-gaga-green-day-stevie-nicks-and-more-to-perform-at-la-wildfires-benefit-concert-3829759">第一波演出名单已于上周确认</a>。</p><p>迄今为止，该法案中最知名的明星包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rod-stewart">罗德·斯图尔特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-perry">凯蒂·佩里</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">乔尼·米切尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">红辣椒乐队</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">斯汀</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">史蒂维·尼克斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">绿日乐队</a>，更多的演员将在法案中公布。未来几天。门票将于 1 月 22 日开始发售，您可以通过 Ticketmaster 获取门票并<a href="https://fireaidla.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处进行捐款</a>。</p><p>昨晚（1 月 19 日），由 AEG Presents 联合主办的活动在社交媒体上宣布奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 已加入 1 月 30 日演出名单的最新成员。</p><p>音乐会将在两个场地同时举行：起亚论坛和 Intuit Dome。每个场地的确认阵容尚未公布。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFBez9iS_qM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,